name: Blue Shell Sparkle
description: A beautiful exclusive handmade jewelery set. This is a one off design that features shaped shell richly dyed blue with 100% natural dyes, and accented with wire work and glitter. They are complemented with clear and blue glass beads and finished with silver plated chain. The earrings and bracelet are also finished with silver plated findings. This is a stunning set that would compliment any outfit or skin tone. Comes packaged in a classy black box that would make a wonderful gift, to your friends or even yourself...

name: Hot Pink
description: A stunning one off design that features shaped shell dyed hot pink with 100% natural dyes and complemented with wire work in lilac wire. It is suspended on a silver plated chain. Set also features matching bracelet and earrings that also have silver plated findings. It is packaged in a classy black gift box that makes this a wonderful gift, even if it's just to yourself.

name: Crackling Red
description: A beautiful one off jewellery set comprising of earrings and necklace that have black coloured hypoallergenic and nickel free findings. They feature stunning red glass crackle beads (hence the name) that reflect light like no other beads that i have seen. They are also complemented by red glass jewels encircled in silver. This is a very special set that would add sparkle to any outfit. Comes packaged in a lovely gift box, making it the perfect present.

name: The Blues
description: A gorgeous one off set in pastel blues. This comprises of earrings and necklace in the most beautiful blue cubes of glass and complimenting blue iridescent seed beads. Some of the cubes are pale blue of exquisite clarity, and the others are clear cubes with a delicate swirl of blue in the centre. The jewellery is finished of with black coloured hypo-allergenic and nickel free findings. This is perfect for anyone who likes their jewellery contemporary, but with a timeless class about it. The set comes packaged in a beautiful gift box which makes it a perfect gift, especially for treating yourself.

name: Statement Squiggles
description: If you are looking for something different, then this set is it. Like all of our jewellery this is a one off piece. This set comprises of a necklace and earrings that feature stunning turquoise wirework, turquoise glass seed beads and ice blue beads that have an iridescent shine. This statement piece of jewellery comes in a beautiful gift box which makes this a perfect gift. Guaranteed to turn even the simplest outfit into a showstopper...
